text: Osselle-Routelle is a commune. It is in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in the Doubs department in east France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Osselle (the seat) and Routelle.Arrêté préfectoral 21 December 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Doubs
title: Osselle-Routelle
